[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0482","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0482.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0767","title":"IBM AIX 与 Sun Solaris LC_MESSAGES libc 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris（7.0、2.6、SunOS 5.7）及 IBM AIX 4.2.1 的 C 语言标准库 libc 及配套工具（ufsrestore、rcp）在处理 LC_MESSAGES 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当用户通过 telnetd 等远程登录服务连接到目标系统，且客户端传递了超长 LC_MESSAGES 环境变量值时，libc 在解析本地化消息时未对输入长度进行边界检查，导致栈缓冲区溢出，可被利用以覆盖返回地址执行任意代码。该漏洞在 setuid/setgid 程序（如 login）启动时同样可被本地攻击者触发，实现权限提升至 root。攻击者无需身份认证，只需建立网络连接并发送特制环境变量即可完成利用，CVSS v2 评分 7.2（HIGH），危害等级严重。Sun 及 IBM 已分别通过安全公告和补丁修复该漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0767"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.953","remediation":"将 Sun Solaris 升级到 Solaris 7 的推荐补丁簇（如 105396 系列）或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本；IBM AIX 升级到 4.2.1 的官方补丁包（APAR IX####）或升级至 AIX 4.3 以上。临时缓解措施：取消普通用户对 ufsrestore、rcp 等 setuid 程序的执行权限（chmod u-s），并限制环境变量 LC_MESSAGES 的注入，通过应用供应商提供的 libc 环境变量过滤补丁修复缓冲区溢出。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420557&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19217","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e244b55bdff85b2483c0e6a7cecd12f8bee0df6e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0767.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0767","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0767.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/70f84d5684ed60f7a4d0750993d15c30e4fe3bbf/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0767.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w824-xcx7-fxrv/GHSA-w824-xcx7-fxrv.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83063/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0767.json","https://github.com/oneaudit/openpoc/blob/31081b881c22c8096e0ee052413d10a2e364e1d3/stats/stats.go","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0482.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1070","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1070.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1353","title":"Nosque MsgCore 明文密码存储漏洞","description":"Nosque MsgCore 2.14 存在密码明文存储漏洞，管理员密码以明文形式保存在注册表 AdmPasswd 键中，用户密码以明文形式存储在 Userbase.dbf 数据文件中。本地攻击者可通过读取注册表或数据库文件直接获取凭证，进而提升权限并完全控制系统，影响机密性与完整性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1353"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-07","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级至 MsgCore 2.15 或更高版本；如厂商已停止维护，应使用 Windows 注册表 ACL 限制 AdmPasswd 键仅允许管理员读取，对 Userbase.dbf 设置 NTFS 权限仅允许管理员访问并启用 EFS 加密，同时确保服务器物理安全。建议迁移至其他支持安全密码存储的邮件服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93698162708211&w=2","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1353"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1070.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1185","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1185.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1562","title":"gFTP FTP客户端明文密码记录漏洞","description":"gFTP 是一款开源的 FTP 客户端软件。在 1.13 及 2.0.0 之前的其他版本中，程序会将用户登录 FTP 服务器时输入的明文密码直接记录在（1）软件界面的日志窗口中，或（2）写入本地日志文件内，而未做任何加密或掩码处理。该漏洞影响范围涵盖上述存在缺陷的 gFTP 版本用户，主要威胁来自本地场景：攻击者只需在受害用户使用 gFTP 后，直接查看其屏幕上的日志窗口输出，或读取存储在本地磁盘的日志文件，即可获取明文 FTP 凭据。利用方式简单且无技术门槛，无需远程网络访问，属于本地信息泄露类问题，可导致账户凭据被窃取并进一步被用于未授权访问 FTP 服务器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1562"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:43.360","remediation":"升级 gFTP 至 2.0.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复将 FTP 密码以明文记录在日志窗口和日志文件中的问题。若无法立即升级，可在 gFTP 设置中关闭\"保存日志文件\"选项并清除已有的 ~/.gftp/gftp.log 等日志文件中的明文密码，避免敏感凭据泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/2001/dsa-084","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/26915","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/3446","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/770e8f09ce14e637a09c7c619e10772aa6172bea/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1562.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1562","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1562.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e1298ff7aafe81b936ca67ecef34c3124d6c72f0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1562.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/debian_DSA-084.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6prp-p499-7x8q/GHSA-6prp-p499-7x8q.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1562.json","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/2001/dsa-084.data","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000764.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1185.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0725","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0725.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0925","title":"Messagemedia UnityMail 2.0 MIME Header 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Messagemedia UnityMail 2.0 邮件服务器在处理邮件 MIME 头部时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送包含大量 MIME 头部的特制邮件，导致邮件服务进程资源耗尽而崩溃，造成正常邮件收发功能中断。该漏洞影响 UnityMail 2.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0925"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.490","remediation":"该漏洞年代久远（1998年），厂商 Messagemedia 已停止支持 UnityMail 2.0，官方不再提供补丁。建议立即将 UnityMail 2.0 升级或迁移至受支持的邮件列表管理方案（如 Mailman 3 或 GNU Mailman）；若无法替换，在反向代理或防火墙上配置 HTTP 请求头数量限制（如限制单请求 MIME 头不超过 100 个），并限制管理 Web 端口的访问 IP 白名单作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90486243124867&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0925.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0925","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0925.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/263f37bc67cd24fe03a39077d8b57f3001369a95/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0925.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4xw9-c2vm-jq79/GHSA-4xw9-c2vm-jq79.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0925.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1760/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0725.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0725.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1309","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1309.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0926","title":"Apache HTTP Server 1.2.5 MIME Header 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache HTTP Server 1.2.5及更早版本在处理大量MIME头部时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送包含大量MIME头部的特制HTTP请求，导致服务器资源耗尽，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需认证即可远程利用，攻击复杂度低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0926"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-03","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至Apache HTTP Server 1.3.0或更高版本，该版本修复了MIME头部处理中的拒绝服务问题。对于无法升级的旧系统，建议在反向代理层面限制单个请求的HTTP头部数量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T01:37:22.370278420+00:00","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1309.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1309.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1309.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1187","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1187.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1564","title":"FreeBSD NFSv3 系统 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 3.2 及部分其他版本中存在拒绝服务漏洞。本地用户可通过大量进程并发访问 NFS v3 挂载目录，触发内核 panic 导致系统崩溃。该漏洞利用条件为拥有本地用户权限，无需特殊系统调用或提权操作，攻击复杂度低。受影响系统包括 FreeBSD 3.2 系列版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1564"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:43.607","remediation":"升级至 FreeBSD 3.2-RELEASE-p10 或更高版本（含修复补丁）；或在 /etc/sysctl.conf 设置 kern.maxprocperuid 限制单用户进程数，并通过 /etc/exports 限制 NFS v3 挂载访问权限作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/26166","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/770e8f09ce14e637a09c7c619e10772aa6172bea/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1564.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1564","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1564.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/12e9f9121122940a38e93216069cda4e01d5b051/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1564.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mqjc-cjrv-6894/GHSA-mqjc-cjrv-6894.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1564.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x85000/84436/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/d32e82aba4856f40aba2bd65020401cfada1e743/1999.tsv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1187.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1148","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1148.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1516","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16328,\"outputTokens\":46,\"totalTokens\":16374}}","description":"TenFour TFS Gateway SMTP 邮件服务器 3.2 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者通过向 SMTP 服务的 MAIL FROM 命令中发送超过 128 字节的特制字符串即可触发该溢出，导致邮件服务器崩溃，并可能进而执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 TenFour TFS Gateway SMTP 3.2 的服务器，未经身份认证的远程攻击者即可利用，无需特殊权限或交互条件。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1516"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:36.473","remediation":"TenFour 官方已在 TFS SMTP Gateway 4.0 中修复该缓冲区溢出漏洞。建议立即将 TenFour TFS Gateway SMTP 服务器从 3.2 升级至 4.0 或更高版本。如暂时无法升级，可通过在防火墙或邮件网关处对 SMTP 连接中 MAIL FROM 命令的数据长度进行限制（拒绝超过 128 字节的字符串）作为临时缓解措施，并监控邮件服务器日志以发现异常连接断开。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93677241318492&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c271719fd48dcc28619dc324e441b822d7b4bace/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1516.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1516","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1516.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1516.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/907ae4099f60f85a9473cd7e47129d370c445f83/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x657-67f8-62qq/GHSA-x657-67f8-62qq.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1516.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/T/tfs_smtp_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000762.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8200d63179d89b9076027cd96356d55ef8a5349e/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1148.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1073","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1073.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1356","title":"Compaq Insight Manager agent Integration Maintenance Utility 法律通告篡改漏洞","description":"Compaq Insight Manager agent 中的 Integration Maintenance Utility 组件在 SmartStart 4.50 之前版本中存在配置篡改漏洞。该工具可修改 Windows NT 系统的登录法律通知标题（LegalNoticeCaption）和文本（LegalNoticeText），导致安全策略中规定的法律声明被篡改或绕过。攻击者利用该工具可覆盖系统登录时的法律提示内容，使其不符合企业安全合规要求，从而削弱系统安全管理机制。此漏洞需要本地访问权限，危害程度中等，影响使用 Compaq Insight Manager agent 的 Windows NT 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1356"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:15.973","remediation":"升级 Compaq Insight Manager agent 至 SmartStart 4.50 或更高版本，该版本修复了 Integration Maintenance Utility 可被伪造请求修改 Windows NT 法律声明的问题。如无法升级，建议限制对 Compaq Insight Manager agent 管理端口的网络访问权限，仅允许受信任主机连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93646669500991&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93637792706047&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93759822830815&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7763.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1356.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1356","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1356.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1356.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p5mv-6mvr-j99h/GHSA-p5mv-6mvr-j99h.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87889/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1356.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000761.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5cf7a56c-2fdc-4fd8-b7ba-076f2fd947b8.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1073.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0244","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0244.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0685","title":"Netscape Communicator EMBED 标签缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.06至4.61版本在处理HTML的EMBED标签中的pluginspage选项时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可构造恶意网页，诱使用户访问后触发缓冲区溢出，导致浏览器崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响Netscape Communicator 4.x系列多个版本，CVSS评分5.1，危害等级中等。建议用户升级至不受影响的版本或更换其他浏览器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0685"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.657","remediation":"Netscape Communicator 已停止维护多年，建议立即卸载该软件，改用 Mozilla Firefox、Google Chrome 等现代浏览器。如因遗留系统必须使用，可在浏览器设置中禁用插件加载功能，或通过注册表禁用 EMBED 标签的 pluginspage 参数解析，同时避免访问不可信网站。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/618","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19486","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/985d46f062894917f05cdf3d64399a32839d12b7/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0685.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0685","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0685.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5d448b12fda744aa8491fddc8705260f2b4289f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0685.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5bd4fceb27857756215e988f4824b12d3de84ec1/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qr94-86r9-f9hg/GHSA-qr94-86r9-f9hg.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0685.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0244.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0244.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0244.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0970","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0970.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1129","title":"Cisco Catalyst 2900 VLAN交换机 802.1q未授权VLAN遍历漏洞","description":"Cisco Catalyst 2900 系列虚拟局域网（VLAN）交换机存在 IEEE 802.1q VLAN 遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过在 trunk 标记中伪造 VLAN 标识符，向目标 VLAN 注入特制的 802.1q 帧，从而跨越 VLAN 边界访问本应隔离的网络资源。该漏洞允许攻击者绕过 VLAN 隔离机制，实现未授权的跨 VLAN 通信，可能导致敏感信息泄露。攻击者无需认证即可利用此漏洞，影响范围广泛。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1129"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.940","remediation":"在 Cisco Catalyst 2900 系列交换机的 trunk 端口上启用 802.1Q 原生 VLAN（native VLAN）隔离，将管理流量与用户 VLAN 分离，并为 trunk 链路配置明确的 allowed VLAN 列表（switchport trunk allowed vlan 仅放行必要 VLAN）。同时升级交换机 IOS 至修复该 802.1Q 标签伪造遍历问题的版本（如 12.0(5)WC 及以上），无法立即升级时关闭不必要的 DTP 自动协商（switchport mode trunk + switchport nonegotiate）以缓解未授权 VLAN 注入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cisco.com/univercd/cc/td/doc/product/lan/28201900/1928v8x/eescg8x/aleakyv.htm","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/26008","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/615","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3294","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1129","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/3bc9583077e9d7007badef726c5b3560d73fb205/1999/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/7d67702de1c8e6c388afcd41c6fc66f9bddaa76f/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-11xx/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1129.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0970.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0400","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0400.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0705","title":"ISC INN inews 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ISC INN（InterNetNews）2.2 版本中的 inews 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该程序用于向 Usenet 新闻服务器投递文章，攻击者可通过网络向目标系统发送特制的新闻文章内容触发溢出，无需身份认证即可利用。成功利用可导致远程代码执行或服务拒绝，影响运行该版本的 Linux 服务器及其上承载的新闻服务。CVSS v2 评分为 7.5（高危），攻击向量为网络，攻击复杂度低，无需权限即可实施。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0705"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.177","remediation":"立即将 ISC INN 升级至 2.2.1 或更高版本（官方已修复该缓冲区溢出），Red Hat Linux 6.0 用户应通过 up2date 或 rpm 命令安装厂商提供的 inn 安全更新包（如 inn-2.2-3 以上）。如暂时无法升级，可将 inews 二进制文件权限设为 0750 并归属至受限新闻组用户组，移除其他用户的执行权限，同时限制本地不可信用户登录以缓解被利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/616","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19480","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/9fb3a936a0c1d10acf1532bf38ee04d3d8b03656/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0705.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0705","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0705.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/30f77465b94d71209b45a239e791a1fe062c9e8b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0705.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/c4492e06ae2b58d2cc1a5b6e3d1be4567633e24b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-43p9-vj97-wmgv/GHSA-43p9-vj97-wmgv.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/inn.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0705.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/616/info.html","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990907.data","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0400.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0202","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0202.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0670","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer Eyedog ActiveX 控件缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 中的 Eyedog ActiveX 控件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页诱导用户访问，触发 ActiveX 控件的缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上以当前用户权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 IE 4.0/5.0 等早期版本，无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击者只需诱导受害者打开包含恶意代码的网页即可触发。CVSS 评分 4.0，属于中等严重度漏洞，微软已发布补丁修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0670"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.737","remediation":"建议立即卸载或禁用 Eyedog ActiveX 控件，在 Internet Explorer 中通过“Internet 选项”→“程序”→“管理加载项”禁用 Eyedog 控件，或直接卸载相关软件；若必须使用 IE，请升级至 IE 6 SP1 及以上版本并安装微软发布的安全补丁 MS99-032 (MS99-032) 修补该漏洞，同时建议在防火墙层面禁用 ActiveX 控件下载作为临时缓解措施","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-064.shtml","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-032","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/3dcf4a672831d0af7dbd00779c08b91c153bbd3e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0670.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0670","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0670.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/512c773c61886081b2589de76a8cfde795349819/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0670.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3c5965e4a3ad0d0b437f880f71224c9e3d8d5fd5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vw7j-x4wv-gff4/GHSA-vw7j-x4wv-gff4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0670.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88352/info.html","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0202.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0196","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0196.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0669","title":"微软 Internet Explorer 4/5 ActiveX 'Eyedog' 控件安全标记错误导致远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4/5 中的 Eyedog ActiveX 控件被错误标记为\"安全可脚本化\"，导致远程攻击者可通过网页诱导用户访问，利用该控件执行任意系统命令。漏洞影响 IE 4.0、5.0 及集成该浏览器的 Windows 95/98/NT 系统，攻击者无需认证即可在用户权限下运行代码。Bubbleboy 蠕虫即利用此漏洞通过 HTML 邮件自动传播，无需用户点击附件。该漏洞源于 ActiveX 安全模型缺陷，微软后续通过安全补丁修复并改进了 ActiveX 签名验证机制。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0669"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.617","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Internet Explorer 6 或更高版本，或安装 Microsoft 安全更新 MS99-037 为 Eyedog ActiveX 控件设置 killbit 以禁用该控件。在 IE 中将 Internet 区域的安全级别设为「高」并禁用「对标记为可安全执行脚本的 ActiveX 控件执行脚本」选项，可临时缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-064.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19487","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8d0ba8eaeba3ff3558e6044a19d5b454dcc12f33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0669.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0669","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0669.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/512c773c61886081b2589de76a8cfde795349819/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0669.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3c5965e4a3ad0d0b437f880f71224c9e3d8d5fd5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m9vr-8q37-f2rh/GHSA-m9vr-8q37-f2rh.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0669.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--231fc8ca-ffbe-47b7-994f-ed5754a27cb7.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0196.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0196.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0196.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1289","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1289.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1027","title":"Solaris 部分 setuid 程序权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统中某些 setuid 程序由于对用户输入或环境变量处理不当，存在权限提升漏洞。本地已认证用户可借助特洛伊木马或不当的环境配置，使这些以 root 权限运行的程序执行其指定的命令，从而获取系统最高权限。攻击者需具备本地登录权限并能影响相关程序的执行环境方可利用该漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1027"],"sources":["avd","cve"],"published":"1999-09-01","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"应用 Sun 官方提供的相应补丁，或将存在问题的 setuid 程序移除 setuid 位，并限制普通用户对关键环境变量的修改以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T14:35:27.209486259+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1027","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/640"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1289.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0864","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0864.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1014","title":"Solaris 7.0 /usr/bin/mail -m 参数本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 系统自带的 /usr/bin/mail 程序在处理 -m 命令行参数时存在缓冲区溢出缺陷。本地普通用户可构造超长的 -m 参数内容，覆盖栈上返回地址，从而在本地以特权（如 root）身份执行任意代码，实现本地权限提升。攻击者需具备本地登录或命令执行权限方可触发该漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1014"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"1999-09-01","updated":"2026-07-19","remediation":"升级到 Solaris 7 已修复该问题的补丁版本（Sun 官方建议安装 Solaris 7 Maintenance Update 或对应内核补丁簇），或限制对 /usr/bin/mail 的 setuid 权限并避免以特权身份调用该命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T12:18:30.252471918+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1014","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/608"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0864.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0864.toml"}]